    <string name="onboarding_p1_title">Obuyambi bw\'omukugu mu nsawo yo</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p1_body">Mira kintu ekikola okukebera ekitunula ekifaananyi ky\'omulamwa gw\'olubuto naawe ne kiteesa oba omulwadde asaanidde okuweerezebwa. Okusalawo kwo okw\'eddagala kukyali mu mukono gwo.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p2_title">Amatendeka asatu amangu</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p2_body">Tegeka omulwadde n\'okoma omulundi gumu. Mira eddako bifaananyi bisatu mu kasera akamu, eronda ekisinga obulungi, n\'eyolesa amagezi n\'akabonero k\'obwesige. Ggwe osalawo eky\'okukola ekiddako.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p3_title">Ekyama kyo kya kusooka</string>
    <string name="onboarding_p3_body">Ebifaananyi by\'abalwadde bisigala ku ssimu eno. Mira tebiweereza wonna okuggyako bw\'osalawo.</string>
