    <string name="help_heatmap_title">Mappu y\'ebbugumu kiki?</string>
    <string name="help_heatmap_body">Langi etadde waggulu eraga we Mira yatunula bwe yali asalawo. Ebifo eby\'ekitangaala bye bitundu Mira bye yalowoozaako nti bikulu. Bwe kifo ky\'ekitangaala bwe kiba ku mulamwa gw\'olubuto era nga kikwatagana n\'ekyo ky\'olaba nga acetowhite, ebivudde bisingayo okwesigibwa. Bwe biba ku speculum oba awalala, twala ebivudde n\'obwegendereza era olowooze okuddamu okuba ekifaananyi.</string>
    <string name="help_confidence_title">Obwesige butegeeza ki?</string>
    <string name="help_confidence_body">Obwesige bwe nga Mira bw\'enesigayo eky\'okuddamu, okuva ku 0 okutuuka ku 100%%. Waggulu wa 80%% kya maanyi. Wansi w\'omugibo gw\'oteeka mu Ntegeka (eya kawefube 65%%), Mira ejja kuteeka ebivudde nga tebikakata era ekusabe okuddamu okuba ekifaananyi. Okusalawo kwo okw\'eddagala kusinga obukulu w\'enamba.</string>
